Class Event

java.lang.Object
Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Event>
class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Event>
Represents a customer interaction. Implements comparable, which compares the event by time and customer ID.
